data.description: Picture yourself unwinding as you watch the sun dip below the horizon the colors reflecting off of the Lewiston Hill and the Snake River. Every evening becomes a personal painting. During the day adventure awaits! Bring your water toys and launch them easily from the Southway Access boat launch. Explore the river at your leisure, creating memories that will last a lifetime. With two living spaces, you can entertain guests, create a cozy reading nook, or enjoy family movie nights. Whatever your lifestyle, this versatile home has something for you!
